title: Frontend Publishing Pro v2.82 - Premium WordPress Plugins
description:
If you want to give your users the ability to create posts from the front-end area then Frontend Publishing Pro is the perfect solution for you. It works well with custom post types/taxonomies and comes with a simple drag and drop interface for easy form building. Thanks to the included shortcodes you can deploy this plugin on your WordPress website in just a few minutes. Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
